PASFMT is a Pascal "pretty-print" program that is invoked as
 
    !PASFMT.X source_fid TO|ON|OVER newsource_fid
 
There are options (such as indenting level) inside the program
that can only be changed by a recompile of PASFMT.
HELP file for: PASFMT.X
 **************************************************************
 *                                                            *
 *  Copyright (c) Bull HN Information Systems Inc., 1989      *
 *                                                            *
 **************************************************************
08/27/82
The change is to be able to left shift text on lines as well as
right shift text. Comments will not be left shifted.
CHANGES
Dave Henderson, Marketing Software Support Services, LADC
